Junard Erasmus was last seen with his mother at the local taxi rank on Saturday. CAPE TOWN - Police are searching for a two-year-old boy who went missing in Delft. Junard Erasmus was last seen with his mother at the local taxi rank on Saturday. The little boy, who can't speak, was wearing a striped t-shirt, navy pants and takkies at the time.   (Edited by Thapelo Lekabe)